Package se.jguru.nazgul.core.algorithms.api.trees.path

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Path<S extends Comparable<S>>
    Generic immutable Path, defining a single continuous list of segments.
    SemanticPath<E extends Enum<E>,SegmentType extends Serializable & Comparable<SegmentType>>
    An extension to Path where all segments have a semantic meaning, defined by the values of an Enum.
